
CoreGraphics
============


1. First install the following packages

	$ sudo aptitude -y install libx11-dev libxt-dev libxtst-dev libcairo2-dev liblcms1-dev

2. Install Back framework:

	gnustep/core/back$ make
	gnustep/core/back$ sudo make install

3. Install Opal framework (CoreGraphics and CoreText):

	gnustep/dev-libs/opal/Source$ make
	gnustep/dev-libs/opal/Source$ sudo make install

